snippet.title: Forgotton Anne - Launch Trailer [PEGI]
snippet.description:
Imagine a place where everything that is lost and forgotten goes; old toys, letters, single socks. The Forgotten Lands is a magical world inhabited by Forgotlings; creatures composed of mislaid objects longing to be remembered again.

Buy now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/542050/Forgotton_Anne/

Buy now on Xbox One: https://www.microsoft.com/en-gb/store/p/Forgotton-Anne/C1XJKZ9JSPHN

Buy now on PS4: https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/product/EP0082-CUSA08146_00-FORGOTTONANNE001
